s-of-the-stone-age-frontman-reveals-cancer-treatment" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a> ）。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Queens of the Stone Age 主唱 Josh Homme 谈论他的癌症康复和新专辑 |英国独立电视台新闻" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/273tXFUAQE4?start=2&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>霍姆告诉<em>英国独立电视台新闻</em>，他现在“感觉是我这一年来感觉最好的”，并表示他的孩子们帮助他度过了艰难时期。</p><p> “宽泛地说‘黑暗时代来临’是可以的，但我想我比以往任何时候都更想寻找光明，你知道吗？”您可以在上面观看完整的视频采访。</p><p> 2022 年 3 月，法院授予 Homme 对他与前妻<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brody-dalle">布罗迪·达尔 (Brody Dalle)</a>共同抚养的三个孩子的临时唯一合法监护权，等待监护权听证会。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/josh-homme-shares-rare-statement-on-legal-battle-with-ex-wife-brody-dalle-3421938">Homme 随后就此事发表了一份罕见的声明</a>，确认达勒不被允许联系家人，包括 Homme、他的父母和前夫妇的三个孩子。</p><p>两人的争执导致双方都<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/josh-hommes-children-file-restraining-order-against-him-3042418">向对方提交了限制令</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brody-dalle-testifies-against-josh-homme-during-domestic-violence-trial-3145871">指控对方进行人身攻击</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3456320" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3456320" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3456320" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Queens-of-The-Stone-Age-Andreas-Neumann-1-1.jpg" alt="《石器时代的女王》专辑评论" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Queens-of-The-Stone-Age-Andreas-Neumann-1-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Queens-of-The-Stone-Age-Andreas-Neumann-1-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Queens-of-The-Stone-Age-Andreas-Neumann-1-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Queens-of-The-Stone-Age-Andreas-Neumann-1-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nm