23/11/itzy-lia-hiatus-blossom-171123-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/itzy-lia-hiatus-blossom-171123-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/itzy">ITZY</a>成员 Lia 发布了一首新的独奏曲目，并宣布她将在乐队即将发行的专辑和世界巡演中保持休息状态。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/itzy-kill-my-doubt-cake-interview-3475493">ITZY 谈“消除我的怀疑”：“在尝试新事物之前，你总是会有怀疑，对吧？”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p> 11 月 17 日， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/jyp-entertainment">JYP 娱乐公司</a>发表<a href="https://fans.jype.com/BoardView?BoardName=itzy_NOTICE&amp;Num=912&amp;DivisionId=&amp;SearchField=&amp;SearchQuery=" target="_blank" rel="noopener">声明</a>，向歌迷通报了这位歌手的最新状况，此前她于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/itzy-lia-hiatus-over-extreme-levels-of-anxiety-3499414">今年 9 月因“极度焦虑”而中断演出</a>。</p><p> “目前，莉亚在进行预定活动时出现紧张和焦虑症状。经专业医疗机构检查，她被诊断<a href="https://www.soompi.com/article/1626950wpp/itzys-lia-to-continue-hiatus-through-new-album-and-world-tour-unveils-solo-track-and-letter-for-fans" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>为</em></a>焦虑症，目前正在集中治疗。”</p><p> “经过与Lia和成员们的充分讨论，决定Lia将缺席2024年1月[ITZY]新专辑的制作以及世界巡演，以恢复健康为首要任务， ”JYP继续说道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="ITZY LIA“Blossom”歌词视频" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dnXyghQd2O8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>经纪公司接着介绍了Lia的新单曲《Blossom》，该歌曲同时在YouTube上公开。这首歌将作为 ITZY 一月份即将发行的专辑的一部分正式发行。</p><p> “<em>我当时怎么样？我当时怎么样？ / 我怎么样？我当时怎么样？我当时怎么样？ /那个还没有绽放的人/那个最后绽放的人，</em> ”她在副歌中唱道。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://www.soompi.com/article/1626950wpp/itzys-lia-to-continue-hiatus-through-new-album-and-world-tour-unveils-solo-track-and-letter-for-fans" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Soompi 报道</a></em>，这位歌手还在该团体的 Instagram 帐户上上传了一封手写的致粉丝的信，将《Blossom》描述为一首“充满了我想向粉丝表达的真诚”的歌曲。</p><p> “我保证会以更好、更健康的方式回归，足以报答MIDZY在我们无法共度的这段时间给予的支持！”利亚继续说道：“感谢您一直以来对我的信任和等待。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Czu6QIJShss/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C56